Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所謂的守墓者指的是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀 真是幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…你真好看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很榮幸得到您的讚賞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面小姐是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫艾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面是個意為面有疤痕的綽號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並不是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說疤面 以前別人是怎麼稱呼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}殺人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繼續回溯再之前的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\alpha&HFF}{\t(1,1,\alpha&H00)}死神 {\alpha&HFF\t(800,800,\alpha&H00)}不是人 {\alpha&HFF\t(2400,2400,\alpha&H00)}疤面 {\alpha&HFF\t(3200,3200,\alpha&H00)}瑪麗亞 {\alpha&HFF\t(4200,4200,\alpha&H00)}石頭腦袋 {\alpha&HFF\t(5300,5300,\alpha&H00)}死神 {\alpha&HFF\t(6300,6300,\alpha&H00)}疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你最初的名字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不介意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:00:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣才是守墓者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有著完美的善良卻沒有任何的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還是守墓者嗎
